=begin pod
=head1 Bitfields

=head2 GtkBuilderClosureFlags

The list of flags that can be passed to gtk_builder_create_closure().

New values may be added in the future for new features, so external
implementations of L<|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gnome::Gtk4::R-BuilderScope> should test the flags
for unknown values and raise a C<GTK_BUILDER_ERROR_INVALID_ATTRIBUTE> error
when they encounter one.

=item C<GTK_BUILDER_CLOSURE_SWAPPED>; The closure should be created swapped. See
  g_cclosure_new_swap() for details.
=end pod

